nul
NUL
CON
PRN
AUX
com[0-9]
lpt[0-9]

# Backups and Archives
*.bak
*_backup_*
backend_backup_*/
backups/
backend/data/backups/
archive/
*.tar.gz
*.zip

# ========================================
# PERSONAL/USER DATA - NEVER TRACK
